Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Imagine planning for a peaceful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}boat trip to Papikondalu, one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}of Andhra Pradesh s most
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}beautiful spots, only for your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}boat to suddenly break down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}water! That s exactly what
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}happened to 89 tourists recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}leading to an urgent rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}operation. This wasn t just
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}a minor hiccup reports say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}the boat developed a snag
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}while heading towards Papikondalu, turning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}a relaxing journey into a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}tense wait for help. Luckily,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}all 89 people were rescued
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}safely, but the incident has
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}big consequences. Boat services from
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}the Gandiposamma Temple point, usually
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}buzzing with activity, have been
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}completely stopped. Think of it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}like when your favorite bus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}route gets suspended after an
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}incident, leaving many people looking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}for other ways to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Authorities are now looking into
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}what went wrong and conducting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}a fresh safety check for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}all other boats. Why is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}this a big deal? Papikondalu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}is part of the Papikonda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}National Park, a huge area
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}known for its nature and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}animals. It s a key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}spot for tourism and local
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}livelihoods. Whenever such an incident
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}happens, it raises questions about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}how safe these trips truly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}are. What improvements do you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}think are needed to make
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}sure these scenic boat rides
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.71,0:01:31.71,CTA,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Subscribe for more breaking news!